{"tid":1192385,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4/PC] Monster Hunter World [320] 9/6一齊出去行街好無?","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T12:37:49.000Z","uid":8429,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"60135a881aa2cd09162101721cd1f493200babdb","tid":1192385,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NaFhxfk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNaFhxfk.jpg&h=7ed6f1b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<ins><strong>網上獵人經驗心得</strong></ins><br />\n<strong>Monster Hunter World官網</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgame.capcom.com%2Fmanual%2FMHW%2Fzh-hant%2Fps4&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=de88ecc7\" target=\"_blank\">http://game.capcom.com/manual/MHW/zh-hant/ps4</a><br />\n<strong>中文Wiki</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mhchinese.wiki\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mhchinese.wiki&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=881b6fb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mhchinese.wiki</a><br />\n<strong>日本Wiki</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://mhwg.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhwg.org%2F&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=790616bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhwg.org/</a> (較常用)<br />\n<a href=\"https://game8.jp/mhw/196165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame8.jp%2Fmhw%2F196165&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=0ee599c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://game8.jp/mhw/196165</a><br />\n<strong>台灣網站教學</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26page%3D%26snA%3D136459%26last%3D&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=ef38dd8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;page=&amp;snA=136459&amp;last=</a><br />\n<strong>配裝模擬器 日中英文對照 Skill simulator</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://mhw.wiki-db.com/sim/?hl=zh-hant#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmhw.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F%3Fhl%3Dzh-hant%23&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=fc6a928d\" target=\"_blank\">http://mhw.wiki-db.com/sim/?hl=zh-hant#</a><br />\n<strong><strong>配裝器使用教學</strong></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=05786&amp;snA=145099\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D05786%26snA%3D145099&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=9ddbe5cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=05786&amp;snA=145099</a><br />\n<strong>傷害模擬器</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://kuroyonhon.com/mhw/d/dame.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkuroyonhon.com%2Fmhw%2Fd%2Fdame.php&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZFIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=89451536\" target=\"_blank\">http://kuroyonhon.com/mhw/d/dame.php</a><br />\n<strong>***新手獵人Q&amp;A***</strong></div><br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩咩武器好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：去鍛練場試手感，獵人冇廢裝。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：一開始用咩裝好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：下位睇防禦力就可以，一係就飛雷龍。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：騰龍裝點整？</ins></strong><br />\nA：打普貝就可以攞到料，而且係自由任，幾時打都得！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：玩男角定女角？</ins></strong><br />\nA：只有外觀分別。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點搵集會區域號碼？</ins></strong><br />\nA：禁option之後禁三角<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咩武器高輸出？</ins></strong><br />\nA：十隻手指各有長短，用剋屬就可以。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：有無人開個新手群？</ins></strong><br />\nA：冇，有嘢請直接問。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解連唔到線？</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為要俾錢買PS Plus。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：噴血少左點算好？</ins></strong><br />\nA：買個紅色鏡片眼鏡試吓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：傷害數字可唔可以整走？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整走。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：鎖定有冇得用3DS果種？</ins></strong><br />\nA：設定有得整。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解入唔到某啲朋友開嘅任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：低進度入唔到高進度個任，要先觸發劇情，搵到見到條龍，可以發出SOS訊號既位，之後quit任再重開就可以一齊玩。亦都可以等低進度果個睇完cut scene，其他朋友就可以係外面任務板join番。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：特典邊度拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係屋仔問管家貓。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：開左角色之後,可唔可以重設?改唔改到名？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請再開多過角色。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：設置地的營區喺邊？</ins></strong><br />\nA：地圖右上方。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：再開新角色，之前beta報酬同特典有冇得再拎？</ins></strong><br />\nA：有巴打試過有。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：冇香港PSN，係咪要買多次？</ins></strong><br />\nA：唔需要，可以開個香港account set常用ps4就可以用有買嘅account玩。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：連線打同solo打有咩分別？</ins></strong><br />\nA：連線會變2.6倍血（網上流傳），所以連線最好齊人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：我想問某種素材點有？</ins></strong><br />\nA：獵人嘅萬能圖鑑可以幫到你，再唔係問埋個位係農場旁邊位師傅睇睇。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解用網捉唔到龍？</ins></strong><br />\nA：請盡快做完自由任完成新手教學。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：啲調查任點出架，仲有邊到開架？</ins></strong><br />\nA：調查任係打完隻怪就會出（細怪都會），而開任就要先去1樓調查資源管理所登錄任務，每個任都有金、銀或者銅嘅特別獎勵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：雌火龍???個任點做?</ins></strong><br />\nA：周圍探索搵雌火痕跡，夠一半佢會叫你返去打一隻蠻顎，打完搵埋剩返果半，儲夠就開櫻火。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁搵啲痕跡有無得快d既方法?</ins></strong><br />\nA：有，佢出既位其實得幾個點，你自己記得左，搵完無即退任重開。當然你要先入一次記低。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：Juno係咩?</ins></strong><br />\nA：滅燼龍，你試下連續讀100次，愈讀愈快就會知。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點開麒麟任？</ins></strong><br />\nA：係你打完下位風漂龍之後，去生物學者個邊接自由任。第一個自由任係兩星嘅捕捉搔鳥，打完再返去生物學者接下一個自由任。跟住重覆步驟，捉土砂龍，浮空龍。直到捉埋慘爪龍，就接到個麒麟任。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：咁上位嘅麒麟任呢？</ins></strong><br />\nA：主線打完古龍之後去珊瑚台地8區同12區到搵佢啲痕跡，搵到某個程度就開比你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：500萬道具包點拎</ins></strong><br />\nA：去小屋個管家禁追加內容，無嘅話就等多陣再搵，個活動壞壞地。<br />\n`<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：上下位/ab混裝出唔出到套裝技</ins></strong><br />\nA：可以<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：點解唔整TG GP</ins></strong><br />\nA：因為無必要，有咩想問有怪想打，係呢度出句聲，大把巴絲打答你幫你。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>Q：激運劵滿左點算？</ins></strong><br />\nA：手持5張激運劵再攞每日登入獎勵就會激運劵變飯劵，所以想繼續激運就請先用左佢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新Post Template:<br />\n右上角三粒點＞以此內容建立新主題"},{"pid":"2a5055d22e76f6fdbfb1ae9330b93110e50ef350","tid":1192385,"uid":60556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"新手留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a43c521557dc1b6191e2f7b329e1f68102d9fbc","tid":1192385,"uid":142416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:44:38.000Z","msg":"唔好：負皮<br />\n好：正皮"},{"pid":"ff68817efc4f6b99da47384af036521d2acb150e","tid":1192385,"uid":26475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:48:08.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正皮"},{"pid":"ad9775edf20592c948deab592274d0f823a14824","tid":1192385,"uid":164761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:48:37.000Z","msg":"有冇人斬樹?"},{"pid":"ca6b57b2bf6cb7c8781f6aab86c2f796c9341ce7","tid":1192385,"uid":8429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:49:41.000Z","msg":"數學大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1192390/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1192390/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"cbcbee2bc72be79e2446961ec4822a7a906d82a5","tid":1192385,"uid":87915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n祝自己千其唔好中 解放珠 菇珠 鐵壁珠 跑者珠 防禦性能珠"},{"pid":"5c2b5818f8328bda1cfabff005de3b628c8e177d","tid":1192385,"uid":8088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:14:32.000Z","msg":"打完今晚 聽日一齊出街！"},{"pid":"dfdda5a1e93617755e3ca2bd6bce402dea0f2d60","tid":1192385,"uid":49697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"有冇場 有冇巴絲玩緊有位可以john<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/